OL,5, A former head of the BBC has said it   
OL,6, was a mistake to take Gary Lineker off 
OL,7, air following the presenter's criticism
OL,8, of government asylum policy.           
OL,10,FGreg Dyke's comments come as the BBC's 
OL,11,Fflagship football show Match of the Day
OL,12,Fdescended into crisis, with staff      
OL,13,Fwithdrawing in support of Lineker.     
OL,15,FThe show's six main pundits and its    
OL,16,Fentire commentary team have stepped    
OL,17,Fback from Saturday's programme.        
OL,19,FMr Dyke said the BBC "undermined its   
OL,20,Fown credibility" by suspending Lineker.
